    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just... it feels like a lie to say it's peaceful. i'm scared. i'm scared that if i just stop fighting and let go, it's not going to be peace, it's just going to be gone. like, is there actually any comfort in nothingness, or am i just being told to give up because it's easier for the system?",
